# =============================================================================
# Trivy Ignore File
# =============================================================================
# Add CVE IDs here (one per line) to suppress known false positives
# during vulnerability scanning.
#
# Format:
#   CVE-YYYY-NNNNN    # reason for suppression
#
# Example:
#   CVE-2023-12345    # false positive: not reachable in our usage
#
# Docs: https://aquasecurity.github.io/trivy/latest/docs/configuration/filtering/
# =============================================================================
